  "commit_message": "Add a `#[derive(diesel::sql_types::Enum)]` proc-macro\n\nThis commit adds a derive to map Rust enums to SQL enums by\nautomatically generating the relevant trait implementations for\n`FromSql` and `ToSql`. This hopefully makes it easier to map rust enums\nto database fields. \n\nRelated to #4759",
